      "authorImage": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/osoEnQWphuz4qtQa8CKkvL0Xjcs9IVMOG3zilwp-Gp_MUvxm5AXjKZ0MxZ_1NGugvizOzQ4J8w=s48-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj",
      "text": "Polish women dressing for self-respect rather than vanity is a rare trait today. As Europe modernizes rapidly, do you think Poland can preserve these deep-rooted traditional values, or will they eventually fade? What’s your take?",
      "likeCount": 1,
      "publishedAt": "2026-06-24T03:09:12Z",
      "replyCount": 1,
      "replies": [
        {
          "id": "UgzbSY7fcC6i9fV7zlx4AaABAg.AYQVPVH4Aj3AYYJwoR_5C5",
          "author": "@AmazingGlobalDiscoveries",
          "authorImage": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/T2v50f6Jyxr5W4Rgq36zJV5ZHEJoK26sCLPrt8u9s0ecJuedWFhcgw42MdyvKjOVmgzbVSm3Qw=s48-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj",
          "text": "I think Poland, like many countries in Europe, is changing quickly, but deep values do not disappear overnight. Respect for family, faith, dignity, and modest elegance still feels very strong in many parts of Polish society. Of course, younger generations will bring new lifestyles, but I believe the heart of Polish tradition can survive if people continue to see it as something meaningful, not just old-fashioned. What do you think is the most important value Poland should protect for the future?",
          "likeCount": 0,
          "publishedAt": "2026-06-27T04:02:57Z"
        }
      ]
    },
