          "text": "I agree, those traditions say a lot about the Polish spirit. Milk bars carry a simple but meaningful sense of community, and the empty seat on Christmas Eve is such a powerful symbol of kindness, memory, and hospitality. Poland really has a deep warmth behind its history and traditions.",
